edBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"南泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d4769799aafa427cf0ea1662e42c44188fbcad","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1879a6dc834e9be98e9d79808116864148c6d011","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18112ae2d8c162ac936f609272f92f55d832515c","tid":707061,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"75369fc8419012c2d851a3868bbea1be9f1d19e0","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b49c71c0578ce4ce1b767ea77707f9374f21cf1c","tid":707061,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"意大利今屆影都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地大韓民國又有得踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 意狗酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"當年仲有黑西班牙喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登真係得中學雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"韓國何得何能買到黑哨呀，球證問題關我地韓國叉事"},{"pid":"814a5f38f8264e0e13e458d01c97307b021f267e","tid":707061,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"兩邊都有啦<br />\ncut 晒南韓個d 出來 <br />\n都該都係意狗先咁嬲"},{"pid":"06019c269773eef881f4b30d85e0694b4ddb0624","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"814a5f38f8264e0e13e458d01c97307b021f267e","tid":707061,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"兩邊都有啦<br />\ncut 晒南韓個d 出來 <br />\n都該都係意狗先咁嬲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"睇埋西班牙先啦on9<br />\n踢到爆哂頭都冇犯規<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063cbf7e5980437fcb4bd6e3f0958ce397cb7de9","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"814a5f38f8264e0e13e458d01c97307b021f267e","tid":707061,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"兩邊都有啦<br />\ncut 晒南韓個d 出來 <br />\n都該都係意狗先咁嬲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"2002年的世界盃，韓國對葡萄牙的小組賽中，葡萄牙隊的2名球員遭紅牌判罰出場；16強淘汰賽對義大利時，義大利隊長托蒂（Francesco Totti）也在關鍵時刻遭罰下場；8強賽對西班牙時，裁判更是吹西班牙的2個進球不算。而南韓球員在這3場比賽中，不斷以暴力方式攻擊對方球員，也遭受全世界足球迷與媒體的批評。<br />\n鄭夢準曾表示：「韓國隊能夠在2002年韓日世界盃上殺入4強，當時有國際足協官員在我面前表示，這一切完全靠鄭夢準買通裁判才辦到的，既然我擁有如此通天本事，那當個首爾市長自然易如反掌。」<br />\n他的發言一出，立刻引起韓國民眾譁然，紛紛指責他失言玷汙韓國形象，對當年的參賽選手更是侮辱，挑戰首爾市長的鄭夢準最後落選。"},{"pid":"db55ee284227fea57da82c9d488c8afc85c452d0","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"2002年韓國對義大利的比賽，主裁判是來自厄瓜多的莫雷諾（Byron Moreno）。因為判決偏袒韓國，義大利有些地方還把他的臉印在廁所的牆上來表達不滿。莫雷諾回國之後又惹出爭議，他在一場聯賽中加了十多分鐘的傷停時間，讓地主隊反敗為勝，但卻在正式紀錄上寫比賽只有90分鐘。最後他被厄瓜多足協開除，FIFA執照也被取消，在2003年宣布退休。<br />\n<br />\n南泡狗繼續兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d672784c7c54bf97b6ae647872567808e99ce76b","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/南韓\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93&d=nvueCfnSCfy7NfZdOypNw7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=82a51775\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/南韓</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎觀賞韓狗爭議事項"},{"pid":"cd341f765e8164d816476a38aaafeaf691ec0f5c","tid":707061,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"皇馬球迷：<br />\n球證都質疑，你係咪識球例過球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪向fifa投訴囉，睇下佢會唔會嘔返個四強俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人正怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eebf71ef45884780f6d2e5e3d7f5f86f3328b7","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd341f765e8164d816476a38aaafeaf691ec0f5c","tid":707061,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"皇馬球迷：<br />\n球證都質疑，你係咪識球例過球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪向fifa投訴囉，睇下佢會唔會嘔返個四強俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人正怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"⼁乛<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/203837_4c0a0f7e92232ad5c1ea30b407c12d7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F203837_4c0a0f7e92232ad5c1ea30b407c12d7e.png&h=c2b5dbe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你同樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27ccb19505abc1ced06fbc64e54e3647480fb52","tid":707061,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"